{"tid":2029039,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［文宣方向］正視聽：國安法會喺香港成立‘強力部門’，9成有埋送中權力，根本等於送中法+23條","createTime":"2020-05-22T05:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T07:11:19.000Z","uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d15b62946930a83ac63977746aa27ec44e7233","tid":2029039,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDdfMKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDdfMKe.png&h=aa4f4726&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四、香港特別行政區應當建立健全維護國家安全的機構和執行機制，強化執法力量，加強維護國家安全執法工作。中央人民政府維護國家安全的有關機關根據需要在香港特別行政區設立機構，依法履行維護國家安全相關職責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87-%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSjJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=c5b9962d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%2F&h=17ca38e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87-%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A/</a>"},{"pid":"23ddd1534f19cbb4cd580f5ef198f59309ece9bf","tid":2029039,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"捉哂啲資本家上去好似肖建華咁回血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fa929e27c240d35620e159dc5ef215dbebfaaa","tid":2029039,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:33:05.000Z","msg":"回血劍"},{"pid":"a907e555dd7c389a86542d3e3044950bc92d4982","tid":2029039,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"Terry:<br />\n<br />\n新的「強力部門」，將橫行香港。<br />\n<br />\n對照澳門與大陸的國安部門，從今日文件可以，未來會更黑暗。<br />\n<br />\n兩會指令，香港政府要建立「健全維護國家安全的機構及執法機關」。<br />\n<br />\n意指，會有新的組織出現，實行更強的打壓。<br />\n<br />\n回望，2018年，澳門的「維護國家安全委員會」，有什麼成員？<br />\n<br />\n行政法務司司長、警察總局局長、行政長官辦公室主任、保安司司長辦公室主任、法務局局長、司法警察司司長、行政長官辦公室及保安司司長辦公室各自一個顧問。<br />\n<br />\n今日兩會的文件明確提到，要求行政、司法和立法機關配合執行國安法。<br />\n<br />\n強力部門，如同大陸的「中華人民共和國國家安全部」，權力極高，接近橫行。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，國安部人員，可以進入任何限制進入的區域，可以向所有機構查閱及索取任何檔案。<br />\n<br />\n同時，只要出示相關證件，可以享受所有交通便利，交通工具、通訊工具、任何場所和建築物，都可以被徵用。￼￼<br />\n<br />\n三權分立和一國兩制，已經變成了人所皆知的黑色幽默。誰還相信，一是騙子，二是白癡。<br />\n<br />\n作者 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84-%E5%BC%B7%E5%8A%9B%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80-%E5%B0%87%E6%A9%AB%E8%A1%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2